  "keyFeatures": [
    "Complete REST API coverage for OKX (account, trading, funding, market data, earn, copy trading, grid trading, and more)",
    "High-performance WebSocket client with automatic reconnect, resubscribe, and re-authentication",
    "WebSocket API Client for promise-driven order management over WebSocket connections",
    "Full TypeScript support with type declarations for all requests and responses",
    "Supports all OKX regions: Global (www.okx.com), EEA (my.okx.com), and US (app.okx.com)",
    "Browser support via webpack bundle",
